{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UIEdgeInsets","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is equal to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero"},{"type":"text","text":", viewport"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties such as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centerCoordinate"},{"type":"text","text":" assume a viewport that matches the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"frame from the viewport. For instance, if the only the top edge is inset, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map center is effectively shifted downward."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the map view’s superview is an instance of "},{"code":"UIViewController","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" whose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property is "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the value of this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property may be overridden at any time."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The usage of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsS